column1: #Text=DS : What do they talk about with you ?
#Text=Oh , it can be a various number of things .
#Text=My last client — and I feel kind of bad , because he was willing to take a picture for you with a hood on , but I got really into the session and I was n’t thinking about you ! I ’m sorry !
#Text=But , he has an S&M relationship with his wife , and he has seen Mistresses in the past , and he said that he needs a masturbation therapist .
#Text=“ I ’m masturbating too much and I ’m not able to please my wife when she wants to be pleased , and I want you to discipline me ! ”
#Text=That was an hour and a half session .
#Text=We talked about his masturbation for half an hour , and I asked him , “ Now you ’re not going to go out…when are you going to masturbate next ? ” He said , “ Not this week . ”
#Text=To be honest , it ’s different for everyone and I do n’t care . [ Laughs ] I do n’t personally care when people masturbate , to be quite honest .
#Text=But he felt like this was not the relationship he wanted with his wife , he wanted to tell me about it , and he did n’t want to talk about his wife in session .
#Text=DS : Do you ever get bored listening ?
#Text=Oh , no ! I find it fascinating because everybody is so …
#Text=I think if you ’re really into it , you never get bored .
#Text=I get bored when people are arrogant .
#Text=Sometimes people will top from the bottom , and that bores me .
#Text=DS : Is it pretty obvious when they are not being honest with you ?
#Text=Yeah , when you ’re doing session you are definitely capable of finding out when they are being honest with you .

#Text=I ask them questions , and sometimes when I feel like that , I ’ll start interrogating them so that they ’ll make a mistake because I want to really know what is going on in their head if they are not letting me know .
#Text=That kind of pisses me off a little bit .
#Text=[ Rebecca comes in and tells Alex she has a client for her to meet , so she has to leave shortly ]
#Text=I ’m probably going to have a session , it sounds like .
#Text=But I just wanted to make that point about checking in where people ’s heads are at ; that ’s something that is very important to me .
#Text=I think that is for a lot of people , although I do n’t want to make generalizations because people are in the industry for a lot of different reasons .
#Text=But for me , I find it fascinating where they start out , where they finish .
#Text=Like this guy who was just here , he wants to come back on a regular basis and discipline himself .
#Text=He wants to make his life better ; he wants to become a better person .
#Text=You do n’t get people who come in here that often saying that .
